## Non-negotiables

- Plan mode required for changes touching more than 3 files, public APIs, refactors, or migrations.
- No placeholder comments (`// TODO`, `// implement later`). Ask if you do not have enough context.
- Use `<pkg-mgr>` only; do not introduce alternatives.
- Run the fast verification after every meaningful change.

